  "title": "Senior / Staff Nurse (Palliative Care) - Jurong #HHL",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location</strong>: Jurong</p><p><strong>Salary</strong>: Up to 6K</p><p><strong>Working hour</strong>: 3 shift<br /></p><p>Job Description:</p><ul><li>Provide palliative nursing care in hospital wards and nursing homes.</li><li>Assess, plan, implement, and document patient care with the palliative team.</li><li>Manage medications and syringe drivers.</li><li>Support ward and nursing home staff on end-of-life care.</li><li>Educate caregivers and nursing staff on comfort care and dying process.</li><li>Coordinate care plans and end-of-life transitions to nursing homes or hospices.</li><li>Act as liaison between hospital, nursing home, and palliative care teams.</li><li>Participate in case discussions and provide training to nursing home staff.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min. Diploma in Nursing / Degree</li><li>Has valid SNB / BCLS</li><li>Relevant clinical experience.</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills.</li></ul><p>If interested, please email me at alexgoh@recruitexpress.com.sg or telegram @alexgohhl</p><p>➖</p><p>Alex Goh Hock Leong</p><p>(CEI.No: R1763413 l Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Life Science) | 99C4599)</p>",
